{
	"info": {
		"_postman_id": "a1f4c9e2-7b3d-4e91-8c62-5a0d6e2f1b74",
		"name": "SwiftTrack Courier — REST API v1",
		"description": "Full Postman collection for the SwiftTrack Courier parcel-management REST API (Laravel + Sanctum).\n\n## Getting started\n1. Select the **SwiftTrack (Local)** environment, or just use the collection variables below.\n2. Run **Auth → Login**. The test script automatically stores the returned bearer token in the `token` collection variable, so every other request is authenticated for you.\n3. Run any other request.\n\n## Variables\n| Variable | Default | Notes |\n|---|---|---|\n| `base_url` | `http://localhost:8000/api/v1` | API root |\n| `token` | _(empty)_ | Filled automatically after Login |\n| `tracking_number` | `SWT-20260722-K4F9C2` | Used by public tracking |\n| `parcel_id` / `delivery_id` / `customer_id` / `driver_id` / `branch_id` | `1` | Path ids for detail/action calls |\n\n## Demo logins (all use password `password`)\n- Super Admin: `admin@swifttrack.lk`\n- Branch Manager: `manager.colombo@swifttrack.lk`\n- Dispatcher: `dispatcher.colombo@swifttrack.lk`\n- Driver: `driver1@swifttrack.lk`\n\nEvery request sends `Accept: application/json`. Authenticated requests inherit `Authorization: Bearer {{token}}` from the collection.",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
	},
	"auth": {
		"type": "bearer",
		"bearer": [
			{
				"key": "token",
				"value": "{{token}}",
				"type": "string"
			}
		]
	},
	"event": [
		{
			"listen": "prerequest",
			"script": {
				"type": "text/javascript",
				"exec": [
					""
				]
			}
		}
	],
	"variable": [
		{ "key": "base_url", "value": "http://localhost:8000/api/v1", "type": "string" },
		{ "key": "token", "value": "", "type": "string" },
		{ "key": "tracking_number", "value": "SWT-20260722-K4F9C2", "type": "string" },
		{ "key": "parcel_id", "value": "1", "type": "string" },
		{ "key": "delivery_id", "value": "1", "type": "string" },
		{ "key": "customer_id", "value": "1", "type": "string" },
		{ "key": "driver_id", "value": "1", "type": "string" },
		{ "key": "branch_id", "value": "1", "type": "string" }
	],
	"item": [
		{
			"name": "Auth",
			"description": "Session management. Login is public; the rest require a bearer token.",
			"item": [
				{
					"name": "Login",
					"event": [
						{
							"listen": "test",
							"script": {
								"type": "text/javascript",
								"exec": [
									"const res = pm.response.json();",
									"if (res && res.data && res.data.token) {",
									"    pm.collectionVariables.set('token', res.data.token);",
									"    console.log('Token saved to collection variable `token`.');",
									"}",
									"pm.test('Login succeeded', function () {",
									"    pm.expect(pm.response.code).to.be.oneOf([200]);",
									"    pm.expect(res.success).to.be.true;",
									"});"
								]
							}
						}
					],
					"request": {
						"auth": { "type": "noauth" },
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{ "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" },
							{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"admin@swifttrack.lk\",\n  \"password\": \"password\",\n  \"device_name\": \"Postman\"\n}"
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{base_url}}/auth/login",
							"host": [ "{{base_url}}" ],
							"path": [ "auth", "login" ]
						},
						"description": "Public. Exchanges credentials for a Sanctum bearer token. Rate limited to 10/min per IP plus a 5-attempt lockout per email+IP. A deactivated account returns 422 with the same message as a wrong password.\n\nSwap the email to test other roles (all use password `password`):\n- `admin@swifttrack.lk` (Super Admin)\n- `manager.colombo@swifttrack.lk` (Branch Manager)\n- `dispatcher.colombo@swifttrack.lk` (Dispatcher)\n- `driver1@swifttrack.lk` (Driver)"
					}
				},
				{
					"name": "Me",
					"request": {
						"method": "GET",
						"header": [ { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" } ],
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{base_url}}/auth/me",
							"host": [ "{{base_url}}" ],
							"path": [ "auth", "me" ]
						},
						"description": "Returns the authenticated user with their branch and driver record."
					}
				},
				{
					"name": "Change password",
					"request": {
						"method": "PUT",
						"header": [
							{ "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" },
							{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n  \"current_password\": \"password\",\n  \"password\": \"BrandNew123\",\n  \"password_confirmation\": \"BrandNew123\"\n}"
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{base_url}}/auth/password",
							"host": [ "{{base_url}}" ],
							"path": [ "auth", "password" ]
						},
						"description": "Revokes all other tokens; the current token survives so the caller is not logged out mid-session."
					}
				},
				{
					"name": "Logout",
					"request": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [ { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" } ],
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{base_url}}/auth/logout",
							"host": [ "{{base_url}}" ],
							"path": [ "auth", "logout" ]
						},
						"description": "Revokes only the token used for this request. Other devices stay signed in."
					}
				},
				{
					"name": "Logout all",
					"request": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [ { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" } ],
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{base_url}}/auth/logout-all",
							"host": [ "{{base_url}}" ],
							"path": [ "auth", "logout-all" ]
						},
						"description": "Revokes every token belonging to the user."
					}
				},
				{
					"name": "Forgot password",
					"request": {
						"auth": { "type": "noauth" },
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{ "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" },
							{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"admin@swifttrack.lk\"\n}"
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{base_url}}/auth/forgot-password",
							"host": [ "{{base_url}}" ],
							"path": [ "auth", "forgot-password" ]
						},
						"description": "Public. Always answers 200 with the same message whether or not the address is registered, so staff accounts cannot be enumerated. Rate limited to 6/min."
					}
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"name": "Public tracking",
			"item": [
				{
					"name": "Track parcel",
					"request": {
						"auth": { "type": "noauth" },
						"method": "GET",
						"header": [ { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" } ],
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{base_url}}/track/{{tracking_number}}",
							"host": [ "{{base_url}}" ],
							"path": [ "track", "{{tracking_number}}" ]
						},
						"description": "No authentication. This is what a QR-code scan resolves to. The payload is deliberately reduced — names masked, addresses/phones withheld. Rate limited to 60/min. 404 when no parcel has that tracking number."
					}
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"name": "Dashboard",
			"item": [
				{
					"name": "Dashboard",
					"request": {
						"method": "GET",
						"header": [ { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" } ],
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{base_url}}/dashboard",
							"host": [ "{{base_url}}" ],
							"path": [ "dashboard" ]
						},
						"description": "Figures scoped to the caller's role: Super Admin (whole network + branch_performance), Branch Manager (own branch), Dispatcher (own branch, revenue removed), Driver (own workload). A Driver with no linked driver record receives 409."
					}
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"name": "Parcels",
			"item": [
				{
					"name": "List parcels",
					"request": {
						"method": "GET",
						"header": [ { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" } ],
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{base_url}}/parcels?per_page=25&page=1",
							"host": [ "{{base_url}}" ],
							"path": [ "parcels" ],
							"query": [
								{ "key": "per_page", "value": "25" },
								{ "key": "page", "value": "1" },
								{ "key": "search", "value": "SWT-2026", "disabled": true, "description": "Tracking number, receiver, phone, city, or customer name/code" },
								{ "key": "status", "value": "out_for_delivery", "disabled": true, "description": "pending | picked_up | at_warehouse | out_for_delivery | delivered | failed_delivery | returned | cancelled" },
								{ "key": "priority", "value": "express", "disabled": true, "description": "normal | express | same_day" },
								{ "key": "customer_id", "value": "12", "disabled": true },
								{ "key": "branch_id", "value": "3", "disabled": true, "description": "Ignored for non-admins" },
								{ "key": "driver_id", "value": "7", "disabled": true },
								{ "key": "from", "value": "2026-07-01", "disabled": true, "description": "Booking date range, inclusive" },
								{ "key": "to", "value": "2026-07-24", "disabled": true }
							]
						},
						"description": "List, filter and search parcels. Enable the disabled query params to filter."
					}
				},
				{
					"name": "Create parcel",
					"request": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{ "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" },
							{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n  \"customer_id\": 1,\n  \"branch_id\": 1,\n  \"receiver_name\": \"Kamala Silva\",\n  \"receiver_phone\": \"0771234567\",\n  \"receiver_address\": \"42, Temple Road\",\n  \"receiver_city\": \"Kandy\",\n  \"receiver_postal_code\": \"20000\",\n  \"pickup_address\": \"10, Galle Road, Colombo 03\",\n  \"parcel_type\": \"package\",\n  \"weight\": 2.5,\n  \"length_cm\": 30,\n  \"width_cm\": 20,\n  \"height_cm\": 15,\n  \"delivery_charge\": 750.00,\n  \"cod_amount\": 4500.00,\n  \"payment_method\": \"cash_on_delivery\",\n  \"priority\": \"express\",\n  \"special_instructions\": \"Call before delivery.\"\n}"
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{base_url}}/parcels",
							"host": [ "{{base_url}}" ],
							"path": [ "parcels" ]
						},
						"description": "Book a parcel. weight must be numeric > 0. receiver_phone must be a Sri Lankan mobile (07XXXXXXXX / +947XXXXXXXX / 947XXXXXXXX). Dimensions are all-or-nothing. cod_amount only allowed when payment_method is cash_on_delivery. Inactive/blacklisted customers cannot book."
					}
				},
				{
					"name": "Get parcel",
					"request": {
						"method": "GET",
						"header": [ { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" } ],
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{base_url}}/parcels/{{parcel_id}}",
							"host": [ "{{base_url}}" ],
							"path": [ "parcels", "{{parcel_id}}" ]
						},
						"description": "Full parcel detail."
					}
				},
				{
					"name": "Update parcel",
					"request": {
						"method": "PUT",
						"header": [
							{ "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" },
							{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n  \"receiver_name\": \"Kamala Silva\",\n  \"receiver_phone\": \"0771234567\",\n  \"receiver_city\": \"Kandy\",\n  \"priority\": \"same_day\",\n  \"special_instructions\": \"Updated: leave with security.\"\n}"
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{base_url}}/parcels/{{parcel_id}}",
